  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">‚ùì Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>What is OneLastAI and how does it work?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            OneLastAI is a comprehensive AI platform featuring 24+ specialized AI agents for various tasks including content creation, data analysis, document processing, and more. Each agent is designed for specific use cases and can be accessed through our web interface or API.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>How do I get started with OneLastAI?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Getting started is easy! Sign up for a free account, explore our 24+ AI agents, try our templates library, and start with the free tier. You can upgrade to Pro or Enterprise plans as your needs grow. Check out our tutorials in the Learning Center for step-by-step guidance.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>What AI agents are available on the platform?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            We offer 24+ specialized AI agents including: CineGen (video generation), ContentCrafter (content creation), DataSphere (data analysis), DocuMind (document processing), EmotiSense (emotion analysis), TaskMaster (project management), NetScope (network analysis), and many more. Each agent is optimized for specific tasks.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>What are the pricing plans and what's included?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <strong>Free Tier:</strong> 100 requests/month, basic agent access, community support<br>
            <strong>Pro Plan ($29/month):</strong> 10,000 requests/month, all agents unlocked, priority support, API access<br>
            <strong>Enterprise ($99/month):</strong> Unlimited requests, custom integrations, dedicated support, SLA guarantee
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>How do I integrate OneLastAI into my application?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Integration is straightforward with our REST API. Get your API key from Settings, use Bearer token authentication, and make requests to our endpoints. We provide SDKs for Python, Node.js, and Ruby, plus comprehensive documentation with code examples.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>What if I'm experiencing technical issues?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            For technical issues: 1) Check our status page for known issues, 2) Clear browser cache and cookies, 3) Verify your API key and request format, 4) Check rate limits, 5) Contact our support team at mail@onelastai.com with specific error details.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>How can I get help from the community?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Join our vibrant community forum with categories for General Discussion, Technical Support, Feature Requests, and Showcase. Connect with other developers, share your projects, get tips and best practices, and participate in community challenges.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span>Do you offer training and learning resources?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
